\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f4\fs24\lang1033\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033\i0\b0 Chapter 2 deals with prohibited practices.  These are to be found in the following sections: section 4 which deals with restricted horizontal practices, section 5 with  restricted vertical practices; section 8 with abuse of dominance, and section 9 with pr
