\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f4\fs24\lang1033\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033\i0\b0 On the one hand, it recognizes that the quantity discount may be utilized arbitrarily and without justification in savings affected by quantity sales, to give a discrimination advantage to large buyers over small ones.  This evil it would prohibit.  On the
